@plane z=2 label="Later"
# Later — Backlog / Bets

Not committed. Needs a champion and a spike before Q4 planning.

## swift-graph (new repo)
- Directed/undirected graph with `AsyncSequence` BFS/DFS traversal
- Potential dep for swift-cache invalidation chains
- **Spike:** 3 days to validate API shape

## `@AppDependency` unification
- Single property-wrapper pattern across all CorvidLabs libs
- Replaces ad-hoc KeyPath subscripts in swift-env, swift-cache, swift-pinata
- High leverage if we land it — estimate **5 weeks** full rollout

## swift-qr 2.0 — visionOS
- Spatial QR scanning via ARKit (visionOS 1+)
- Market: devs building spatial commerce apps
- **Owner needed** — nobody has visionOS hardware yet

## Telemetry / Usage Analytics (internal)
- Anonymous `fledge` command usage to guide roadmap priorities
- Privacy-first: opt-in, no PII, hashed repo IDs only
- Needs legal sign-off before any code

